## §3. TECHNICAL DRILL-DOWN — per extension

### §3.1 `.anc` — Identity passport

**Purpose:** Sealed entity boundary. Một entity (persona, cell, governance object) có 1 `.anc` = identity neo bất biến.

**Schema:** `@state sealed | @canonical <id> | @substrate identity | @authority-slot <owner>`

**Sample paths:**
  - `./docs/specs/SPEC_NEN_v1.1.anc`
  - `./docs/specs/natt-os-PLATFORM-SPEC.anc`
  - `./src/cells/cells.cell.anc`

### §3.2 `.si` — Boundary signature

**Purpose:** Hard rule contract per cell. Định nghĩa I/O boundary, forbidden operations, allowed callers.

**Schema:** `<cell-name>.boundary.si` — 1 file per business cell.

**Sample paths:**
  - `./src/thienbang.si`
  - `./src/cells/business/warehouse-cell/warehouse-cell.boundary.si`
  - `./src/cells/business/noi-vu-cell/noi-vu-cell.boundary.si`

### §3.3 `.kris` + `.na` — Memory continuum (legacy → v1.2 R01)

**Purpose:** Sealed persona memory snapshot. `.kris` là format legacy, `.na` là v1.2 R01 (active migration).

**Pattern:** `<entity>khương<semver>.kris` (legacy) → `<entity>khương<semver>.na` (v1.2)

**Sample paths:**
  - `./docs/specs/SPEC_NGON_NGU_v1.2.kris`
  - `./docs/specs/roadloading/đổi sang ngôn ngữ nauion/spec-ngon-ngu-natt-os-v1.1-full.kris`
  - `./docs/specs/natt-os_SATELLITE_COLONY_SPEC.na`
  - `./docs/specs/SPEC_MOMENTS_MODULE_v0.1.na`

### §3.4 `.phieu` — Runtime state

**Purpose:** Mutable P-shell state. `<entity>thịnh<semver>.phieu`. NEN v1.1 §17.2 TwinPersist paradigm — write to `.nattos-twin/khai/<trace_id>.khai` + persist to `.phieu`.

**Sample paths:**
  - `./runtime/audit/src/cells/kernel/audit-cell/scanner/file-extension-validator.khai.result.phieu`
  - `./src/governance/system-state.phieu`
  - `./src/governance/memory/boiboi/boithịnh-plan.phieu`

### §3.5 `.heyna` — Transport signal

**Purpose:** Mạch HeyNa SSE transport. NOT EventBus (which is L1 internal). HeyNa is L2 between cells / between server and client.

**Sample paths:**
  - `./src/governance/audit-log.heyna`
  - `./src/governance/builder-audit-trail.heyna`

### §3.6 `.sira` — DNS namespace anchor

**Purpose:** Kernel entry identity. `nattos.sira` (root) = KERNEL ENTRY INBOUND on `127.0.0.1:3002`. Cells declare `.sira` namespace too.

**Sample paths:**
  - `./nattos.sira`

### §3.7 `.khai` — TouchRecord

**Purpose:** KhaiCell signature mark per SPEC NEN v1.1 §4.1. Field boundary marker — vượt rào → bị mark signature, không bị reject.

**Sample paths:**
  - `./src/cells/kernel/audit-cell/contracts/file-extension-validator.interface.khai`
  - `./src/cells/kernel/audit-cell/scanner/file-extension-validator.khai`
  - `./src/cells/kernel/quantum-defense-cell/bootstrap.khai`

### §3.8 `.thuo` / `.obitan` / `.canonical` / `.ml` — Lower-frequency artifacts

| Đuôi | Count | Notes |
|---|---:|---|
| `.thuo` | 5 | Snapshot 1 thuở (.na đo tại moment) — dùng khi cần freeze field state |
| `.obitan` | 3 | Persona electron-shell phase fragment — vết hằn theo orbital |
| `.canonical` | 1 | Authoritative reference pointer — minimal, critical files |
